Coté view.py:

class RucheView(TemplateView):
    template_name = "ruche.html"

    def add_ruche(request, rucherPk):
        rucheContext = {rucher_pk: rucherPk}
        # Do anything you need to do before rendering template
        return render(request, 'ruche_add_form.html', rucheContext)
     
Coté url.py:
from path.to.my.views import views as ruche_views
...
urlpatterns = [
...
  url(r"^rucher/addRuche/(?P<rucherPk>.*)$", ruche_views.add_ruche),
  ...
]

Dans l'url, tu as (?P<rucherPk>.*) ce qui correspond a ta variable rucherPk dans les paramètre de la fonction add_ruche()
